It asks for clarity in the news about earthquake shocks at the Flegrei Fields to prevent instrumentation and alarm against the tourist industry: to ask in a note is the national and regional president of the Association of Bed &amp; Breakfast and Guest House of Campania (Abbac), Agostino Ingenito.
